{"parentUuid":"8cde937e-0402-423e-974a-4cee3e5e302b","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"97f8e502-2809-4fbe-ae25-bfe99bbaf354","agentId":"a056046afd74f4258","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012Cf1G4ewUSkr9nV1xPLAud","type":"tool_result","content":"335:## Threat Model\n337:Method: STRIDE (Shostack), scoped to **this feature** (GET list + DELETE). Each credible threat names\n365:### STRIDE table\n454:STRIDE THREATS (threat; vector; severity; mitigation + concrete mechanism):\n494:## ASVS Compliance\n497:below. Requirement IDs are cited per threat in the STRIDE table above.\n528:- **Security report clean** → ✓ *Threat Model* + *ASVS Compliance* (parameterized DELETE SQL, admin\n564:  4. Added a **STRIDE** Information-Disclosure row (GET/DELETE DB I/O boundary; Medium; generic-500"}]},"uuid":"35cfd005-925a-46e2-bb3b-232fe98d2e54","timestamp":"2026-07-10T01:55:23.947Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"8cde937e-0402-423e-974a-4cee3e5e302b","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"C:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"cb1e5971-0f87-4706-9a1d-09f830df9e6f","version":"2.1.205","gitBranch":"feature/quota-admin"}
